; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the auto-xact cost derivation for per-unit prices.  When an
; automated transaction copies a posting that has a per-unit cost (@),
; the generated amount carries a price annotation without
; ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT, so the cost is computed by multiplying
; the price by the amount

= /Expenses:Electricity/
    (Budget:Electricity)    1.0

2024/01/01 Electric Bill
    Expenses:Electricity    100 kWh @ 0.72 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Electric Bill         Expenses:Electricity        100 kWh      100 kWh
                                Assets:Cash                  EUR-72       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
                                (Budget:Electricity)        100 kWh       EUR-72
                                                                         200 kWh
end test
